::Feline::

She kept running until she was about a mile away from the Cybetron 
Fire.  She stopped and waited for Skulletron to catch up.  She 
transformed into bot mode and waited.  She had an idea spring into 
her mind.  She would have Skulletron hit her a few times o make it 
look like she had gotten into a fight.  A few bruises would back up 
my story of escape, she thought.  She had a wicked smile on her 
face.  She looked back and waited for him to catch up to her. Then to 
put her plan into action.
